; Coverage test for xact.cc
; Tests the error when a transaction has two postings with null amounts.
; Only one posting with null amount is allowed per transaction.

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food
    Expenses:Rent
    Assets:Cash               $-50.00

test bal -> 1
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 8:
Error: Only one posting with null amount allowed per transaction
end test
